OL,3,C'Selfless' woman born with hole in
OL,4,Cheart 'brings joy' to poorly children
OL,6,FA Newcastle woman who was treated for
OL,7,Fa hole in her heart as a teenager at a
OL,8,FNewcastle hospital now runs a toy
OL,9,Fappeal for the sick children there.
OL,11,FA regular check up when Calli Tully
OL,12,Fwas 17 showed her life was in danger
OL,13,Fand she had to undergo nine hours of
OL,14,Fopen heart surgery at the Freeman
OL,15,FHospital to save her life.
OL,17,FAfter she came home, all she could
OL,18,Fthink about were the children still in
OL,19,Fhospital at Christmas, so she decided
OL,20,Fto bring Christmas to them and began
OL,21,Ffundraising to buy gifts.
