OL,3,C'Selfless' woman born with hole in
OL,4,Cheart 'brings joy' to poorly children
OL,6,FNow aged 27, she has not stopped.
OL,8,FCalli is one of four finalists for the
OL,9,FTyne Tees Fundraiser of the Year - the
OL,10,Fwinner of which will go to London to
OL,11,Fthe Pride of Britain award ceremony.
OL,13,FAfter finding out she needed surgery
OL,14,FCalli said she "didn't want to be here
OL,15,Fanymore".
OL,17,FShe added: "I got a phone call from
OL,18,Fthe Freeman Hospital saying I needed
OL,19,Fto come in for immediate heart surgery.
