OL,3,C'Selfless' woman born with hole in
OL,4,Cheart 'brings joy' to poorly children
OL,6,F"I actually hung up the phone first
OL,7,Fbecause I was so scared and then my
OL,8,FMum came home from work and said, 'we
OL,9,Fneed to go to hospital'.
OL,11,F"So we literally came straight here.
OL,12,FIt was the worst time ever, I
OL,13,Fliterally didn't want to be here any
OL,14,Fmore."
OL,16,FAlthough she had been discharged and
OL,17,Freturned home, she wanted to bring joy
OL,18,Fto the children that were still
OL,19,Fundergoing treatment, so she started
OL,20,F'Calli's Heart Campaign'.
