OL,6,FCalli's next sights are sat on aiming
OL,7,Fto raise money to buy a holiday home
OL,8,Ffor families to visit when they leave
OL,9,Fhospital.
OL,11,FShe said: "I've met families from all
OL,12,Fover the world, some children who have
OL,13,Funfortunately passed away as well and
OL,14,FI've helped them make memories."
OL,16,FMs Woof added: "The fact that at such
OL,17,Fa young age, she chooses to be so
OL,18,Fselfless is truly wonderful.
